---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const posts = [
  {
    href: '/blog/taxas-inpi',
    tag: 'Taxas oficiais',
    title: 'Taxas do INPI 2025/2026: tabela completa e quem tem desconto',
    description: 'Todos os valores oficiais da Portaria GM/MDIC nº 110/2025, o que mudou com a extinção da taxa de concessão e a lista completa de quem pode declarar o desconto de 50%.',
    meta: 'Atualizado em 2026 · 5 min',
    featured: true
  },
  {
    href: '/blog/como-funciona-registro',
    tag: 'Passo a passo',
    title: 'O passo a passo do registro de marca no INPI',
    description: 'Da pesquisa de viabilidade ao certificado válido por 10 anos: as 7 etapas do processo.',
    meta: '4 min',
    featured: false
  },
  {
    href: '/blog/duvidas-frequentes',
    tag: 'Perguntas frequentes',
    title: 'Dúvidas comuns sobre registrar uma marca',
    description: 'CNPJ, prazos, taxas, indeferimento e desconto — respondidas direto.',
    meta: '3 min',
    featured: false
  }
];
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Blog Registrium — Guias sobre registro de marca e taxas do INPI"
  description="Guias práticos sobre taxas do INPI, o passo a passo do registro de marca e as dúvidas mais comuns de quem está protegendo uma marca."
>
  <header class="blog-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <a class="back" href="/">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M19 12H5M11 6l-6 6 6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        Voltar ao site
      </a>
      <span class="pill">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 3l1.9 5.1L19 10l-5.1 1.9L12 17l-1.9-5.1L5 10l5.1-1.9L12 3z" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
        Blog Registrium
      </span>
      <h1>Tudo sobre registrar e proteger sua marca</h1>
      <p>Guias práticos sobre taxas do INPI, o passo a passo do registro e as dúvidas mais comuns de quem está protegendo uma marca pela primeira vez.</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="section article">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid post-grid reveal">
        {posts.map((post) => (
          <a class:list={['post-card', { featured: post.featured }]} href={post.href}>
            <span class="post-tag">{post.tag}</span>
            {post.featured ? <h2>{post.title}</h2> : <h3>{post.title}</h3>}
            <p>{post.description}</p>
            <div class="post-foot">
              <span class="post-meta">{post.meta}</span>
              <span class="post-arrow">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
              </span>
            </div>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section closing">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-card reveal centered">
        <div>
          <h2>Novas publicações em breve</h2>
          <p>Este blog cresce junto com o conteúdo da Registrium — volte sempre para novos guias sobre marcas, propriedade intelectual e o dia a dia do INPI.</p>
          <a class="button button--secondary" href="/#cadastro">
            Preencher cadastro
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
<style>
.blog-hero { position: relative; overflow: hidden; background:
    radial-gradient(120% 90% at 85% 20%, rgba(70,110,230,.26), transparent 55%),
    radial-gradient(90% 80% at 10% 90%, rgba(120,70,200,.22), transparent 60%),
    linear-gradient(125deg, var(--color-navy-950) 0%, var(--color-indigo-900) 55%, var(--color-purple-900) 100%);
  padding: 4.5rem 0 3.5rem; color: var(--color-white); }
.blog-hero .back { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: .5rem; color: var(--color-on-dark); text-decoration: none; font-size: .84rem; font-weight: 600; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; margin-bottom: 1.375rem; }
.blog-hero .back:hover { color: var(--color-white); }
.blog-hero .pill { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: .55rem; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.22); background: rgba(255,255,255,.06); color: var(--color-white); border-radius: 999px; padding: .55rem 1.05rem; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-size: .75rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .13em; text-transform: uppercase; }
.blog-hero .pill svg { width: .95rem; height: .95rem; color: #8fd0f5; }
.blog-hero h1 { color: var(--color-white); font-size: clamp(1.875rem, 4.4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.1; max-width: 47.5rem; margin-top: 1.375rem; }
.blog-hero p { color: var(--color-on-dark); font-size: 1.03rem; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 38.75rem; margin-top: 1.125rem; }

.post-grid { grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 1fr 1fr; }
.post-card { background: var(--color-white); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-md); padding: 1.875rem 1.75rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; text-decoration: none; box-shadow: 0 20px 40px -32px rgba(30,20,80,.4); transition: transform .18s ease, box-shadow .18s ease; }
.post-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 28px 50px -30px rgba(60,40,150,.42); }
.post-card.featured { grid-row: span 2; background: linear-gradient(160deg, #241a52, #12123a); border-color: transparent; color: var(--color-white); padding: 2.25rem 2rem; }
.post-tag { display: inline-flex; align-self: flex-start; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-size: .69rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-violet); background: rgba(138,87,206,.1); border-radius: 999px; padding: .375rem .8rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
.post-card.featured .post-tag { color: #c7b6f5; background: rgba(255,255,255,.1); }
.post-card h2, .post-card h3 { font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: .75rem; color: var(--color-text); }
.post-card.featured h2 { color: var(--color-white); font-size: 1.625rem; }
.post-card:not(.featured) h3 { font-size: 1.16rem; }
.post-card p { font-size: .875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 1.25rem; flex: 1; }
.post-card.featured p { color: var(--color-on-dark); font-size: .94rem; }
.post-foot { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: .75rem; margin-top: auto; }
.post-meta { font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-size: .72rem; color: var(--color-muted); font-weight: 600; }
.post-card.featured .post-meta { color: var(--color-on-dark-soft); }
.post-arrow { width: 2.125rem; height: 2.125rem; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--color-cream); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: var(--color-violet); flex: none; transition: background .15s ease, transform .15s ease; }
.post-card:hover .post-arrow { transform: translateX(3px); }
.post-card.featured .post-arrow { background: rgba(255,255,255,.12); color: var(--color-white); }

.closing { padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 2.5rem; }
.cta-card.centered { position: relative; overflow: hidden; border-radius: 1.75rem; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1); color: var(--color-white); padding: 3.75rem 3.5rem; text-align: center;
  background: radial-gradient(120% 130% at 85% 20%, rgba(120,70,200,.4), transparent 55%), linear-gradient(120deg, var(--color-navy-950), var(--color-indigo-900) 60%, var(--color-purple-900)); }
.cta-card.centered h2 { color: var(--color-white); font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.6vw, 2.625rem); font-weight: 800; }
.cta-card.centered p { color: var(--color-on-dark); font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 34rem; margin: 1.125rem auto 1.875rem; }

@media (max-width: 1040px) { .post-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } .post-card.featured { grid-column: 1 / -1; grid-row: auto; } }
@media (max-width: 560px) { .post-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .blog-hero { padding: 3.25rem 0 2.5rem; } .cta-card.centered { padding: 2.25rem 1.375rem; } }
</style>
